@@TJvSpacer
<TITLEIMG TJvSpacer>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.FormsAndApp.Forms>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Can be used as a spacer on a window.
Description
  TJvSpacer can be used as a spacer on a window. Use this component if you need to create a gap
  between two controls.
  
  Set property Align to position the spacing object on the screen, and set property Spacing to
  determine the size of the control.
  
  Note that you can't place components on a TJvSpacer, and that it has no caption.

